		<div id="comment_body_42806817"><p>I think that's primarily because conspiracy theorists imagine that conspiracies are typically much grander than the ones that exist in reality.  The very nature of a conspiracy tends to keep it small; human nature is not overcome so easily.</p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_42806817">

</div>
</div>

