			<h4><a id="comment_link_42807253" name="comment_link_42807253" href="//science.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=3437457&amp;cid=42807253" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(42807253)" >make a habit of reading pools to get big picture</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_42807253" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 42807253); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>5</a>, Interesting)</span></h4>
