	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_42807399"><p>Conspiratorial Thinking is clear example of the <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dunning%E2%80%93Kruger_effect" title="wikipedia.org">Dunning Kruger</a> [wikipedia.org] effect at work.</p><p>They overestimate their own intelligence or skill, and ignore contrary feedback.  They disavow the intelligence or skill of others.  These people are simply too stupid to invalidate their own hypothesis and recognise the validity of the alternative.</p></div>
	</div>

