			<h4><a id="comment_link_42807599" name="comment_link_42807599" href="//science.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=3437457&amp;cid=42807599" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(42807599)" >Does "Skeptic" == the new "Hacker"</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_42807599" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 42807599); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>5</a>, Informative)</span></h4>
