			<h4><a id="comment_link_42806741" name="comment_link_42806741" href="//science.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=3437457&amp;cid=42806741" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(42806741)" >Re:It is Psychology, Science! Fact!</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_42806741" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 42806741); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>5</a>, Insightful)</span></h4>
